	<div style="text-align:right;">
		ALVES, Gabriela Barreiros<sup>1</sup>; RIBEIRO, Franciele Dalvana<sup>2</sup>; CARVALHO, Ruy Inacio Neiva de<sup>3</sup>		<BR>
